{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8d518117e5","title":"对施复亮的报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9ac2f321cc","index":0,"year":1952,"month":5,"day":5,"articleId":"8d518117e5"}],"tags":[{"id":"5fd56865b0","name":"彭真","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"58204c9e0e","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8d518117e5","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"施复亮，当时任民主建国会常务委员。"},{"id":"8dcb09a0f3","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8d518117e5","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指施复亮1952年4月22日写的《五反后北京工商界的情况和问题的简报》。简报反映的问题是：一、经营管理权问题。二、工人监督问题。三、工资问题。四、房产所有权问题。五、补税问题。六、劳动纪律问题。七、小企业的劳资关系问题。八、资金问题。九、分红与利润问题。十、职工福利问题。"},{"id":"f71a1e1a6b","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8d518117e5","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘，指刘少奇。周，指周思来。14]彭真，当时任中共北京市委书记、北京市人民政府市长。李立三，当时任中央人民政府劳动部部长。"},{"id":"6b34be6baa","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8d518117e5","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"黄敬，当时任天津市人民政府市长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"5df31a8156","type":"title","text":"对施复亮的报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8d518117e5"},{"id":"58204c9e0e","type":"paragraph","text":"刘周阅后，送影真同志处理","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8d518117e5"},{"id":"8dcb09a0f3","type":"paragraph","text":"这是施复亮给劳动部的报告，由季立三以送来的。其中所述的问题应予迅速妥善解决，请彭真同志注意，并请彭告黄敬@注意，在五月份内解决这些问题","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8d518117e5"},{"id":"f71a1e1a6b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8d518117e5"},{"id":"6b34be6baa","type":"paragraph","text":"五月五日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8d518117e5"},{"id":"76bb622172","type":"paragraph","text":"退季立三同志。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8d518117e5"},{"id":"f74b4ddce0","type":"paragraph","text":"施复亮文件已阅，已告彭真同志注意解决这些问题。这些是普遍的问题，中央已指示各地注意妥善解决。施复亮另有关于他对民建会性质任务的新的提纲一件也收到了，尚未研究，便时请告施。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8d518117e5"},{"id":"887531b2ab","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8d518117e5"},{"id":"08db2ec81f","type":"paragraph","text":"五月五日","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8d518117e5"}],"page":{"id":"3bfe4c3d45","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8d518117e5","start":98,"end":99}}}},"__N_SSG":true}